                <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> Caesari divi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Divi Iuli nepoti <lb n="3"/>Augusto <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>maxumo <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>tribun</abbr><ex>icia</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> XXVI co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> IIII
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Es handelt sich wohl um den Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Datierung: zwischen dem 26. 6. 24 und dem 25. 6. 25 (tribun. potest. XXVI).</p>
